This paper is primarily focused on robotics and autonomous assembly, which falls under the category of cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also discusses the use of reinforcement learning and neural networks, which are common topics in the sub-categories of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also mentions the use of CAD data, which is related to computer vision and image processing, and could fall under the sub-category of cs.CV (Computer Vision). Finally, the paper discusses the ability to generalize the assembly controller to changes in object positions, which is related to control systems and could fall under the sub-category of cs.SY (Systems and Control).
